Caption: Audience at the 2nd Institute Day
Description: Sitting (second from right) in the first row: Mr. Y. S. Ramaswamy, the Superintending Engineer of IIT Madras, and his family. Mr. R. Natarajan, in his interview with Prof. Ajit Kolar, mentions that Mr. Ramaswamy came to IIT Madras two years after Natarajan joined. He mentions that Mr. Ramaswamy came from the CPWD to work at IIT.
